16.  booklet, 16 pages printed in colours to show the title, details of the parts, illustrations of models and instructions.
TITLE:-  Tri-ang Regd Trade Mark/ ARKITEX MODERN BUILDING EQUIPMENT HANDBOOK & CATALOGUE of Kits and Accessories.  Made in 1:42 and OO True Scale

fields.title: arkitex scal model construction kit set no. A, ho/oo Scale
fields.location: Museum of Childhood, Creativity Gallery, case 16
fields.marks:
SPOT-ON MODELS BY TRI-ANG
MADE IN NORTHERN IRELAND BY SPOT-ON MODELS LTD
on booklet - LINES BROS GROUP in triangle mark with L. 75M/61 Spot-On Models Limited Castlereagh Road, Belfast.  Printed in England
fields.history_note:
References: Spot-On was one of the trademarks used by Lines Brother Group.
Arkitex was produced in two scales, HO/OO for railways and 1:42 for road ways.  Production began in 1962 and the booklet is dated 1961.

The donor was born in 1959
fields.production_note: Made by: Spot-On Models Ltd, Castlereagh Road, Belfast, Northern Ireland
